NK013(pa)011:0: sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i sbyin sreg bsnyen pa'i kha skong
NK013(pa)011:1: gi ched du byas pa zla ba'i 'od zer zhes
NK013(pa)011:4: nam yang mi 'gyur lhun grub phrin las bzhi //
NK013(pa)011:5: kun khyab ris meda 'gro ba 'dul mdzad pa //
NK013(pa)011:6: bla ma rdo rje sems dpa'i ngo bo la //
NK013(pa)011:7: phyag byas rgyud lung zhi ba'i sbyin sreg bri /
NK013(pa)011:9: / 'dir sa ga zla ba'i sbyin sreg bklag chog mar bkod pa /
NK013(pa)011:10: lo chen rin po che'i gsung gzhir bzhag nas /
NK013(pa)011:11: bsnyen pa'i kha skong sogs mdun bskyed kyi dkyil 'khor dang ma 'brel ba'i tshe /
NK013(pa)011:12: ji ltar bya ba'i rim pa cung zad bsgyur te bri ba la /
NK013(pa)011:13: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhi ba 'bring po'i dkyil 'khor dang sbyar nas ston te /
NK013(pa)011:14: de la thog mar bcas gshoms ni /
NK013(pa)011:15: thab stegs gru bzhi pa rgyar khru do dang dpangs
NK013(pa)011:16: su khru phyed pa'i khar dri dkar po dang ba
NK013(pa)011:18: de'i steng ngos kyi mtha' nas zlum skor gyi mu
NK013(pa)011:19: khyud nag po la yig dang seng mgo spel ba'i
NK013(pa)011:20: nang du 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa bri /
NK013(pa)011:21: de'i lte bar thab khung rtsigs na rgyar khru gang
NK013(pa)011:22: dang dpangs su khru phyed zlum por bslang ba'i phyir
NK013(pa)011:23: bkyed pa'i sor bzhi'i tshad can gyi kha khyer bang
NK013(pa)011:24: rim gsum la / nang nas rim par 'khor lo
NK013(pa)011:25: lcags kyu 'od phreng gis bskor ba'i dbus su srab
NK013(pa)011:26: mthug sor gang tsam pa'i thab mtshan 'khor lo gyis
NK013(pa)011:27: rim gsum la / mtshan pa ste / thams cad kyang tshon dkar pos kha bsgyur ro //
NK013(pa)011:29: thab stegs bri rtsigs gang byed kyang rung zhing /
NK013(pa)011:30: gzhi'i 'khor lo seng spel ba'i mu khyud dang bcas
NK013(pa)011:31: pa bri dus kha khyer gyi 'og tu tshud pas
NK013(pa)011:33: gzhan thams cad sngar dang 'dra bar rdul tshon dkar pos bri bar bya'o //
NK013(pa)011:34: gang ltar yang 'o ma can gyi shing rtse mo'i
NK013(pa)011:35: cha las byung ba'am dgon pa'i ba gci skam gtsang
NK013(pa)011:36: srog chags med pa thab nang du thab las cung
NK013(pa)011:37: zad dma' ba zlum por brtsigs pa'i shar lhor me
NK013(pa)011:38: tshang bca' / stegs bu'i grwar mda' bzhi btsugs pa
NK013(pa)011:39: srad bu dkar pos bsnol mar bran cing steng nas
NK013(pa)011:41: stegs bu'i shar lho'i zur du mda' dar dmar po gzug /
NK013(pa)011:42: thab kyi mdun du stan dkar zhing 'jam pa dang /
NK013(pa)011:43: de'i g.yas g.yon du khru gang ba'i tshad kyi rdzas
NK013(pa)011:44: stegs dang mchod stegs dkar po ste gsum ga la
NK013(pa)011:45: sna tshogs pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa re bri /
NK013(pa)011:46: stan gyi mdun du zheng mtho gang dpangs slob dpon
NK013(pa)011:47: gyi sked pa tsam sleb pa'i me yol gangs ri
NK013(pa)011:48: bris pa bzhag / g.yas phyogs rdzas stegs kyi pad+ma'i
NK013(pa)011:49: lte bar ba las byung ba'i mar khu dgang blugs
NK013(pa)011:50: kyi gzar bu kha sbyar ba dang bcas pa /
NK013(pa)011:51: mdun gyi 'dab mar 'o ma can gyi rtse mo'i
NK013(pa)011:52: cha las byung ba'i yam shing mtho gang ba rtse
NK013(pa)011:54: pad 'dab lhag ma bdun la til dkar /
NK013(pa)011:56: nas dkar dang 'bras dkar gyi chan sogs kha zas dkar po dang /
NK013(pa)011:57: tsan+dana dkar po sogs dri dkar po'i rigs dang /
NK013(pa)011:58: tsam pa ka sogs me tog dkar po'i rigs te
NK013(pa)011:59: thams cad rang bzhin nam bcos pas dkar ba 'das
NK013(pa)011:60: ma 'das kyi khyad par gyis phyi nang nyis rim
NK013(pa)011:61: dang thugs dam bskul ba'i rdzas yungs kar rnams rin
NK013(pa)011:62: po che dkar po'i snod du bsham /
NK013(pa)011:63: g.yon phyogs mchod stegs kyi pad+ma'i lte bar /
NK013(pa)011:64: 'o ma 'bras chan dngul phye me tog dkar po
NK013(pa)011:65: rnams dang bsres pa'i mar dkar gyi 'das gtor zlum
NK013(pa)011:66: po ril bu drug gis bskor ba many+dzi'i steng bkod
NK013(pa)011:67: pa'i mdun du rgyu de las 'jig rten las 'das
NK013(pa)011:69: mdun gyi pad 'dab la rdor dril /
NK013(pa)011:70: de'i g.yas g.yon gyi 'dab mar sman raka /
NK013(pa)011:71: pad 'dab lhag ma lnga la zhabs bsil dang bzhi
NK013(pa)011:72: bsnol gyi mchod rdzas rang bzhin nam bcos pas dkar
NK013(pa)011:73: ba g.yas bskor du bsham zhing las bum kyang ci
NK013(pa)011:74: bder bzhag go // de ltar bshams zin nas cho ga ni /
NK013(pa)011:75: slob dpon chas gos dang rin po che'i rgyan dkar
NK013(pa)011:76: pos brgyan la rdo rje'i skyil krung gis shis pa'i
NK013(pa)011:77: phyogs su kha bltas pas 'dug nas /
NK013(pa)011:78: don gyi sems chos thams cad kyi gshis lugs lhag
NK013(pa)011:79: pa bden pa dbyer med kyi lta ba rtogs shing
NK013(pa)011:80: byang chub kyi sems dang ldan pas /
NK013(pa)011:81: kun slong stongs kyi sems rang gzhan gyi gnod sdig
NK013(pa)011:82: sel bar 'dod pa'i sems zhi zhing dang ba'i sgo
NK013(pa)011:83: nas / ngag sngags rnams phra zhing zhi ba rgyun
NK013(pa)011:84: mi chad par bzla ba'i tshul gyis cho ga'i las
NK013(pa)011:85: nas / la 'jug ste / dzi na dzika ces pas /
NK013(pa)011:86: rang nyid rnam par snang mdzad dkar po zhal gcig
NK013(pa)011:87: phyag gnyis pa'i rnam pas dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgo'i
NK013(pa)011:88: thad du 'khod de sbyin sreg gi las rim la
NK013(pa)011:90: rdo rje thabs kyi rang bzhin ye shes lnga yi ngo bo dang /
NK013(pa)011:91: dril bu shes rab kyi rang bzhin stong nyid chos kyi sgra dbyangs sgrogs pa /
NK013(pa)011:92: gnyis ka'ang don dam pa'i byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin du mos pa brtan par byas la /
NK013(pa)011:94: zhes rdo rje gsor zhing thugs kar 'dzin /
NK013(pa)011:95: badz+ra g+han+de +aah dril bu dkrol zhing dkur brten /
NK013(pa)011:96: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa ga na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)011:97: zhes 'khyud rgya byas te dam tshig gsum dran par bya'o //
NK013(pa)011:98: de nas phyi mchod rnams sgrub thabs ltar brlab cing /
NK013(pa)011:99: sman raka gnyis sngags tsam gyis byin rlabs gso /
NK013(pa)011:100: las gtor dang sreg rdzas rnams la las bum gyi chu 'thor zhing /
NK013(pa)011:103: stong pa'i ngang las ma dang a las nyi zla'i
NK013(pa)011:104: ga'u'i snod du rang gi thugs ka nas gtor ma'i
NK013(pa)011:105: gnas su 'bru gsum dang sreg rdzas kyi gnas su
NK013(pa)011:106: 'bru lnga spros te 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa
NK013(pa)011:107: las zhi ba'i las gtor rin po che'i mchod sdong
NK013(pa)011:108: 'od zer dkar po 'phro ba dang sreg rdzas rnams
NK013(pa)011:109: ro brgya ldan pa'i zag med ye shes kyi bdud
NK013(pa)011:110: rtsi nam mkha' gang bas zhi ba'i las sgrub pa
NK013(pa)011:111: la thogs pa med pa'i nus pa dang ldan par
NK013(pa)011:113: h+aum s+w+aa +aam h+aa zhes bzlas pas byin gyis brlab /
NK013(pa)011:115: stong pa'i ngang las mdun du b+h+r+aum yig 'phro 'dus
NK013(pa)011:116: yongs su gyur pa las 'khor lo'i lte ba la
NK013(pa)011:117: gnas pa'i zhi ba'i thab khung dkar zhing zlum pa
NK013(pa)011:118: kha khyer bang rim gsum dang ldan pa 'od zer
NK013(pa)011:120: rang gi thugs ka nas ram yig thab nang du
NK013(pa)011:121: spros pa las ye shes kyi me 'od dkar po
NK013(pa)011:123: ag+ne ye dz+wa la dz+wa la hum phata /
NK013(pa)011:124: ces rgyun bzhag gam gtsub shing las byung ba'i me du ba med pas spar la /
NK013(pa)011:125: thab kyi me'i dbus su ma dang d+aihls byung ba'i
NK013(pa)011:126: nyi ma dang ra skyes kyi gdan la yig dkar
NK013(pa)011:127: po'i 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las ag+ne de
NK013(pa)011:128: ba ri shi h+aum zhi ba'i me lha dkar po
NK013(pa)011:129: zhi zhing 'dzum pa drang srong gi cha byad can
NK013(pa)011:130: gun+d+he dang bgrang phreng 'dzin pa'i skur gyur /
NK013(pa)011:131: a dar+sha sogs kyis bskur brlab /
NK013(pa)011:132: thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od zer 'phros pas shar lho nas me lha 'khor bcas bzhengs par bsam la /
NK013(pa)011:133: ag+ne de ba sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes se gol bsnol mar gdab /
NK013(pa)011:134: mda' dar dmar pos g.yab cing /
NK013(pa)011:136: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK013(pa)011:137: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs 'byung po che //
NK013(pa)011:138: me lha drang srong bram ze mchog /
NK013(pa)011:139: 'di nyid du ni gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)011:141: ag+ne de ba ri shi dzahdzahsa spyan drang /
NK013(pa)011:146: me lha zhal cung zad gdangs pa sreg blugs kyi bdud rtsi'i rgyun drangs nas gsol bar bsam la /
NK013(pa)011:147: lag gnyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i khu tshur du byas pas dgang blugs bzung nas /
NK013(pa)011:149: zhes g.yas pa'i blugs gzar bdun gyis g.yon pa'i dgang
NK013(pa)011:150: gzar bkang ste rjes gzar bu kha sbyar te pus
NK013(pa)011:151: mo'i nang las mi 'da' bas g.yas bskor gyis /
NK013(pa)011:152: ag+ne de ba ri shi ha bya ka bya di
NK013(pa)011:153: bya bdag cag dpon slob 'khor dang bcas pa'i nad
NK013(pa)011:154: gdon sdig sgrib bar chad mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams
NK013(pa)011:155: cad sh+aan+tim ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)011:156: zhes lan gsum gyis dgang blugs phul /
NK013(pa)011:157: de rjes sngags de kho nas yam shing mar khu
NK013(pa)011:158: bsreg rdzas rnams re re nas lnga'am bdun sogs ji
NK013(pa)011:161: tshangs pa 'jig rten mgon gyi sras //
NK013(pa)011:162: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /
NK013(pa)011:163: 'byung po yongs su skyabs pa'i phyir //
NK013(pa)011:164: thugs rje'i dbang gis skur sprul pa //
NK013(pa)011:165: rig sngags sprul pa drang srong tshul //
NK013(pa)011:166: nyon mongs sreg pa'i shes rab 'od //
NK013(pa)011:167: bskal pa'i me bzhin gzi brjid 'bar //
NK013(pa)011:168: mngon shes rdzu 'phrul zhabs dang ldan //
NK013(pa)011:169: thabs kyis sprul pa'i theg pa chibs //
NK013(pa)011:170: bgrang phreng 'dzin cing rig sngags gsung //
NK013(pa)011:171: bdud rtsi'i bcud ldan gun+d+he bsnams //
NK013(pa)011:172: chos kyi bdud rtsis yongs la bsil //
NK013(pa)011:173: nyes pa'i skyon bral tshangs par spyod /
NK013(pa)011:176: zhi ba brnyes kyang thugs rje che //
NK013(pa)011:177: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK013(pa)011:179: yungs kar thab tu gtor zhing /
NK013(pa)011:180: na mo rig pa'i rgyal po khyod kyis las thams
NK013(pa)011:181: cad byed pas bsreg rdzas lha'i zhal du 'bul ba
NK013(pa)011:182: dang / me nyid ye shes kyi mer byin gyis
NK013(pa)011:183: brlabs nas dpon slob 'khor dang bcas pa'i nad gdon
NK013(pa)011:184: sdig sgrib thams cad zhi ba'i phrin las mdzad du
NK013(pa)011:186: de dag sbyin lha ste 'jig rten pa'i me lha mchod pa'i cho ga'o //
NK013(pa)011:187: de nas sreg lha zhes pa 'das pa'i me lha mchod pa ni /
NK013(pa)011:188: me lha'i lto ba yangs shing rgya che ba'i dbus
NK013(pa)011:189: su b+h+r+aum yig 'phro 'dus yongs su gyu pa las
NK013(pa)011:190: / b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he ye shes rin po
NK013(pa)011:191: che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa
NK013(pa)011:193: ye shes phyogs bzhi dbus brtags te /
NK013(pa)011:195: nyi zla pad+ma rin po che //
NK013(pa)011:196: zhes pa'i bar gyis gsal btab la /
NK013(pa)011:197: rang gi thugs ka nas yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa
NK013(pa)011:198: gnyis 'thon te so so'i gdan steng du 'khod pa
NK013(pa)011:200: rtsibs bzhi'i shar du tha tha /
NK013(pa)011:204: rtsibs mchan gyi shar lho'i gdan la ka tsa /
NK013(pa)011:208: gru chad kyi shar lho'i gdan la pa ya /
NK013(pa)011:220: sgo bzhi'i shar sgor nga sha /
NK013(pa)011:224: de rnams kha dog dkar po so so'i gdan la 'khod par gyur /
NK013(pa)011:226: ces brjod pas yig 'bru rnams las 'od zer 'phros /
NK013(pa)011:227: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs /
NK013(pa)011:229: slar 'dus nas yig 'bru rnams la thi ma pas yongs su gyur pa las /
NK013(pa)011:241: h'u l+aa s+ye sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK013(pa)011:243: t+r+aam m+aa le sa ma ya hoh h+r+aim ha h+aum pad+ma pra da ma /
NK013(pa)011:244: h+r+aim g+ai ti ra go ya ham /
NK013(pa)011:246: am nirti r+aa ga ya me /
NK013(pa)011:247: mee tri d+ha ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)011:248: dzahd+d+h+au pe pra we sha ya /
NK013(pa)011:249: th+l+him nis+sa ram b+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)011:251: h'u swa r+aa dza ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)011:252: bam d+ai pa su gi r+ai /
NK013(pa)011:253: mum sh+r+ai +aam r+aa ga ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)011:256: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta +aah mu ne krem s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)011:257: mu ne h'u trum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)011:263: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai dz+wa l+ai ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)011:265: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai dz+wa l+ai ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)011:267: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai dz+wa l+ai ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)011:269: ma h+aa karma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai dz+wa l+ai ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)011:270: ces so so'i sngags brjod pas /
NK013(pa)011:271: bcom ldan 'das dpal rnam par snang mdzad la sogs
NK013(pa)011:272: te bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK013(pa)011:273: lha tshogs thams cad sku mdog dkar po g.yas 'khor
NK013(pa)011:274: lo dang g.yon rang rtags 'chang ba so so'i gdan
NK013(pa)011:275: la bzhugs pa'i sku las 'od zer dkar po'i phreng
NK013(pa)011:276: ba mkha' khyab tu spro pas zhi ba'i phrin las
NK013(pa)011:278: gdan la rdzogs dang sems dpa'i tshul /
NK013(pa)011:280: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK013(pa)011:281: zhes pa'i bar sku mdog ston pa'i rkang pa gnyis dor bas gsal la gdab /
NK013(pa)011:282: rigs lnga'i phyag rgya gnas lngar gtugs la /
NK013(pa)011:283: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)011:285: +aa dar+sha sa ma t+aa pra t+ya be k+sha na kri t+y+aa nush+tha na zhes pas dbang bskur /
NK013(pa)011:286: rdo rje'i phyag rgya gnas gsum du gtugs la /
NK013(pa)011:287: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)011:289: w+aa ka tsit+ta zhes rgyas gdab /
NK013(pa)011:290: thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od zer 'phros pas rang bzhin
NK013(pa)011:291: gyi gnas nas ye shes kyi 'khor lo spyan drangs
NK013(pa)011:292: par bsam la // bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs shing //
NK013(pa)011:293: rang rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK013(pa)011:295: tshogs mchog dkyil 'khor gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)011:296: e h+ye hi +aa na ya dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes
NK013(pa)011:297: pas dam tshig pa dang gnyis su med par gyur
NK013(pa)011:301: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi ljags rdo rje 'od
NK013(pa)011:302: kyi sbu gu can gyis sreg blugs kyi bdud rtsi'i
NK013(pa)011:303: rgyun drangs nas gsol bar bsam la /
NK013(pa)011:305: ces lan gsum gyis bkang ba'i dgang blugs kha sbyar ba /
NK013(pa)011:306: lung las bshad pa'i zhi ba zhe gnyis kyi spyi sngags /
NK013(pa)011:307: bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na d+h+aa
NK013(pa)011:308: tu +aah zhes pa'i mthar spel tshig sngar ltar btags
NK013(pa)011:310: de nas yam shing mar khu sogs sreg rdzas gzhan
NK013(pa)011:311: rnams lha rang rang gi sngags kyis so sor gtso
NK013(pa)011:312: 'khor gyi 'gros sbyar te 'bul ba'am mi nus na
NK013(pa)011:313: / bo d+hi tsit+ta spyir bargya'am nyer gcig tsam bcu
NK013(pa)011:314: tshan re re'i mthar spel tshig sngar ltar sbyar nas
NK013(pa)011:316: bsnyen pa'i kha skong gi dbang du byas na /
NK013(pa)011:317: rnal 'byor pa bdag gi lha nye bar ma bsgom pa /
NK013(pa)011:318: snying po dag par ma bgrangs pa /
NK013(pa)011:321: ting nge 'dzin thang lhod du gyur pa la sogs
NK013(pa)011:322: pa'i dam tshig nyams chag zhig ral du gyur pa
NK013(pa)011:323: thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)011:326: dzi na dzika sa pa ri w+aa ra ma h+aa ba lid+ta kh+aa his las gtor dang /
NK013(pa)011:328: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa his sman raka phul nas //
NK013(pa)011:329: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK013(pa)011:330: zhes sogs kyis bstod la thab khung du yungs kar 'thor zhing //
NK013(pa)011:331: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK013(pa)011:332: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i sbyin sreg 'bul //
NK013(pa)011:333: bdag gis zhi ba'i phrin las mthar phyin nas //
NK013(pa)011:334: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par mdzod //
NK013(pa)011:335: ces gsol ba btab pas lha tshogs rnams kyi sku las 'od zer dkar po 'phros /
NK013(pa)011:336: bsgrub bya la reg pas nad gdon sdig sgrib thams cad zhi bar bsam mo //
NK013(pa)011:337: de nas gtang rag gi mchod bstod dang bzod gsol byas la /
NK013(pa)011:338: me lha'i ye shes pa rang bzhin gyi gnas su gshegs /
NK013(pa)011:339: dam tshig pa gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa rang la thim par bsam mo //
NK013(pa)011:341: ag+he ye dz+wa la dz+wa la h+aum phata /
NK013(pa)011:342: ces blugs gzar bdun gyi mar khus me gsos te
NK013(pa)011:343: 'jig rten pa'i me lha sngar bzhin gsal bar bsam
NK013(pa)011:344: la / ag+ne de ba ri shi ha bya sogs kyis bsreg rdzas lhag rnams phul /
NK013(pa)011:346: ag+ne de ba ri shi ma h+aa ba lid+ta kh+aa hi /
NK013(pa)011:348: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa his las gtor dang sman raka phul /
NK013(pa)011:352: me lha ye shes pa rang gnas su gshegs //
NK013(pa)011:353: dam tshig pa 'bar ba'i rnam par gyur par bsam
NK013(pa)011:354: la las kyi rjes bsdu zhing bsngo smon shin brjod
NK013(pa)011:356: zhes pa 'di yang rang dang skal mnyam 'ga' la
